name: Verify rejecting the "extra cup of Mocha" keeps cart unchanged
description:
As a user
  I want to reject the "Lucky Day" offer
  So that my cart does not include any unwanted items
descriptionHtml:
As a user
I want to reject the "Lucky Day" offer
So that my cart does not include any unwanted items

testStage.description:
As a user
  I want to reject the "Lucky Day" offer
  So that my cart does not include any unwanted items

steps.name: Given  I am on the menu page
When  I click on "Flat White" drink 3 times
Click on cup with title: Flat White
Click on Cup body
Click on cup with title: Flat White
Click on Cup body
Click on cup with title: Flat White
Click on Cup body
Then  I verify "Lucky Day" modal appears with extra cup of Mocha
When  I choose to skip the lucky day offer
Click «Nah, I'll skip.»
Click on the element
Then  I verify Mocha is not in the cart
When  I clear the cart
And  I click on the following drinks:
Click on cup with title: Americano
Click on Cup body
Click on cup with title: Espresso Macchiato
Click on Cup body
Click on cup with title: Espresso
Click on Cup body
Then  I verify "Lucky Day" modal appears with extra cup of Mocha
When  I choose to skip the lucky day offer
Click «Nah, I'll skip.»
Click on the element
Then  I verify Mocha is not in the cart
And  I verify the following drinks are in the cart:
